y at settlement\n    52в†’\n    53в†’**Changes**:\n    54в†’- `services/backend/src/worker/closecall-clock.ts`: In `settleRound()`, after the DB settlement update, added user transaction writes using raw `sql` tagged template (consistent with file's existing pattern вЂ” this worker receives `sql` not the `Db` object). For each entry in `greenEntries` and `redEntries`: (a) one `join` row (amount = entry.amountLamports), (b) one outcome row вЂ” `win` with payout = `floor((entryAmount / sidePool) * netPool)` if on winning side, `loss` with original amount if on losing side, or `refund` with original amount if `isRefund`. Game = \"closecall\", match_id = round_id (minute timestamp). All writes use `ON CONFLICT DO NOTHING` for idempotency. Inserts are parallelized via `Promise.all`.\n    55в†’\n    56в†’**Check**: `pnpm lint` вЂ” pass. `pnpm typecheck` вЂ” backend passes. Pre-existing platform typecheck error in `CloseCallRoundPage.tsx` (not related to changes).\n    57в†’\n    58в†’## Iteration 4 вЂ” 2026-03-19T18:53:47Z вЂ” OK\n    59в†’- **Log**: iteration-004.log\n    60в†’\n    61в†’## Iteration 5 вЂ” API route GET /profile/transactions\n    62в†’\n    63в†’**Item**: [engine] API route `GET /profile/transactions`\n    64в†’\n    65в†’**Changes**:\n    66в†’- `services/backend/src/middleware/jwt-auth.ts`: Added `requireAllMethods?: boolean` config option. When true, JWT verification applies to all HTTP methods (not just POST). Backward compatible вЂ” defaults to false.\n    67в†’- Created `services/backend/src/routes/profile.ts`: New route handler with `GET /transactions`. Extracts wallet from JWT `c.get(\"wallet\")`. Supports query params: `cursor` (pagination by id), `limit` (default 20, max 50), `game` (accepts both DB names like `lord` and frontend names like `lord-of-rngs`). Maps response: `game` в†’ frontend names (`lord` в†’ `lord-of-rngs`, `closecall` в†’ `close-call`), `amountLamports` as string, `matchId` camelCase, `createdAt` ISO string. Returns `{ transactions: [...], nextCursor: string | null }`.\n    68в†’- `services/backend/src/index.ts`: Registered profile routes at `/profile` with `requireAllMethods: true` JWT middleware.\n    69в†’\n    70в†’**Check**: `pnpm lint` вЂ” pass. Backend `tsc --noEmit` вЂ” pass. Pre-existing platform typecheck error in `CloseCallRoundPage.tsx` (not related).\n    71в†’\n    72в†’## Iteration 5 вЂ” 2026-03-19T18:57:43Z вЂ” OK\n    73в†’- **Log**: iteration-005.log\n    74в†’\n    75в†’## Iteration 6 вЂ” SOL/USD price endpoint\n    76в†’\n    77в†’**Item**: [engine] SOL/USD price endpoint вЂ” `GET /price/sol-usd`\n    78в†’\n    79в†’**Changes**:\n    80в†’- Created `services/backend/src/routes/price.ts`: New route handler with `GET /sol-usd`. Uses `@pythnetwork/hermes-client` HermesClient to fetch SOL/USD price (feed ID `0xef0d8b...`). In-memory cache with 60s TTL вЂ” returns stale cache on fetch error (graceful degradation). Response: `{ price: number, expo: number, updatedAt: string }`. Returns 503 if no price available at all.\n    81в†’- `services/backend/src/index.ts`: Imported `createPriceRoutes`, registered at `/price` with no auth middleware (public endpoint).\n    82в†’\n    83в†’**Check**: `pnpm lint` вЂ” pass (0 errors). Backend `tsc --noEmit` вЂ” pass. Pre-existing platform typecheck error in `CloseCallRoundPage.tsx` (not related).\n    84в†’\n    85в†’## Iteration 6 вЂ” 2026-03-19T19:05:00Z вЂ” OK\n    86в†’- **Log**: iteration-006.log\n    87в†’\n    88в†’## Iteration 6 вЂ” 2026-03-19T19:00:41Z вЂ” OK\n    89в†’- **Log**: iteration-006.log\n    90в†’\n    91в†’## Iteration 7 вЂ” Wire ProfileTransactions to real API\n    92в†’\n    93в†’**Item**: [frontend] Wire `ProfileTransactions` to real API\n    94в†’\n    95в†’**Changes**:\n    96в†’- `apps/platform/src/features/player-profile/types.ts`: Updated `ProfileTransaction` type to match API shape вЂ” added `TransactionEvent` type (`join`/`win`/`loss`/`refund`), replaced `outcome`/`wagerAmount`/`payoutAmount`/`netResult`/`timestamp` fields with `event`/`amountLamports`/`txSig`/`createdAt`.\n    97в†’- `apps/platform/src/features/player-profile/utils/mock-simulation.ts`: Updated `recordTransaction()` to produce new-shaped `ProfileTransaction` objects (join + outcome rows per game result, amounts in lamports-as-string).\n    98в†’- Created `apps/platform/src/features/player-profile/hooks/useTransactions.ts`: New hook that fetches from `GET /profile/transactions` with JWT Bearer auth, supports cursor-based pagination and game filter, handles abort cleanup.\n    99в†’- `apps/platform/src/features/player-profile/components/ProfileTransactions.tsx`: Rewrote to use `useTransactions` hook. Removed mock `getTransactions` import. New columns: Time, Game (linked to match page), Event (color-coded), Amount (SOL). Added loading skeleton (shimmer animation), empty state, and \"Load more\" button for pagination.\n   100в†’- `apps/platform/src/features/player-profile/components/ProfilePage.tsx`: Removed `address` prop from `<ProfileTransactions>` (now uses JWT, not address).\n   101в†’- `apps/platform/src/features/player-profile/hooks/index.ts`: Exported `useTransactions` hook.\n   102в†’- `apps/platform/src/features/player-profile/index.ts`: Exported `TransactionEvent` type.\n   103в†’- `apps/platform/src/index.css`: Replaced old outcome/net styles with event type styles (win=green, loss=pink, join=muted, refund=blue), added match link hover, loading skeleton shimmer animation, load more button styles.\n   104в†’\n   105в†’**Check**: `pnpm lint` вЂ” 0 errors (145 pre-existing warnings). `tsc --noEmit` вЂ” only pre-existing CloseCallRoundPage error (not related).\n   106в†’\n   107в†’## Iteration 7 вЂ” 2026-03-19T19:09:37Z вЂ” OK\n   108в†’- **Log**: iteration-007.log\n   109в†’\n   110в†’## Iteration 8 вЂ” SOL amount display with USD estimate\n   111в†’\n   112в†’**Item**: [frontend] SOL amount display with USD estimate\n   113в†’\n   114в†’**Changes**:\n   115в†’- Created `apps/platform/src/features/player-profile/hooks/useSolPrice.ts`: New hook that fetches `GET /price/sol-usd` from backend, caches price in React state, refreshes every 60s. Returns `number | null` вЂ” null when unavailable (graceful degradation).\n   116в†’- `apps/platform/src/features/player-profile/hooks/index.ts`: Exported `useSolPrice` hook.\n   117в†’- `apps/platform/src/features/player-profile/components/ProfileTransactions.tsx`: Updated `formatSol()` to accept optional `solUsdPrice` param. When price is available, displays `\"0.50 SOL (~$75.00)\"`. When null, shows SOL only. Added `useSolPrice()` call in component, passed to all amount cells.\n   118в†’\n   119в†’**Check**: `pnpm lint` вЂ” 0 errors. `pnpm typecheck` вЂ” only pre-existing CloseCallRoundPage error (not related).\n   120в†’\n   121в†’## Iteration 8 вЂ” 2026-03-19T19:11:52Z вЂ” OK\n   122в†’- **Log**: iteration-008.log\n   123в†’\n   124в†’"}]},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"session_id":"b99e2185-20b1-487e-a0a4-b3fb9a756d45","uuid":"ae8d2315-c1fe-41cd-8696-78dbe5fe2204","timestamp":"2026-03-19T19:12:07.098Z","tool_use_result":{"type":"text","file":{"filePath":"/workspaces/rng-utopia/docs/specs/008-user-profile/history.md","content":"# Implementation History вЂ” 008-user-profile\n\nIteration log for the autonomous spec loop. Each entry records what was\nattempted and whether it succeeded. The agent reads this file at the start\nof every iteration to understand prior context.\n\n---\n\n## Iteration 1 вЂ” Migration + DB functions\n\n**Item**: [engine] Migration + `insertUserTransaction` / `getUserTransactions`\n\n**Changes**:\n- Created `services/backend/migrations/008_user_transactions.sql` (named 008 since 007 already existed for `round_entries`). Table schema: `id BIGSERIAL PK`, `wallet TEXT`, `game TEXT`, `match_id TEXT`, `event TEXT`, `amount_lamports BIGINT`, `tx_sig TEXT`, `created_at TIMESTAMPTZ`. Indexes: `idx_user_tx_wallet_created`, `idx_user_tx_match_id`. UNIQUE constraint on `(wallet, match_id, event)` for ON CONFLICT DO NOTHING idempotency.\n- Added to `db.ts`: types `UserTransactionEvent`, `UserTransaction`, `InsertUserTransactionParams`. Functions `insertUserTransaction()` (INSERT ... ON CONFLICT DO NOTHING) and `getUserTransactions()` (cursor-based pagination, optional game filter, max limit 50).\n\n**Check**: `pnpm typecheck` and `pnpm lint` вЂ” both pass.\n\n## Iteration 1 вЂ” 2026-03-19T18:43:27Z вЂ” OK\n- **Log**: iteration-001.log\n\n## Iteration 2 вЂ” Coinflip write paths\n\n**Item**: [engine] Coinflip write paths вЂ” creator join, opponent join, win+loss at settlement\n\n**Changes**:\n- `services/backend/src/routes/create.ts`: Added `insertUserTransaction()` call after round INSERT to write creator `join` row (wallet, game=\"coinflip\", matchId, amountLamports).\n- `services/backend/src/worker/pda-watcher.ts`: Added `db: Db` to `PdaWatcherDeps` interface. In `handleCoinflipChange()`, after lock detection, fire-and-forget write of opponent `join` row using decoded match data (opponent wallet, entryAmount, matchId from on-chain account).\n- `services/backend/src/worker/settle-tx.ts`: In `settleMatch()`, after `settle_confirmed` operator event, write `win` row (payoutAmount, txSig) and `loss` row (original entryAmount, txSig) in parallel via `Promise.all`. Loser derived as the non-winner of creator/opponent.\n- `services/backend/src/index.ts`: Pass `db` to `createPdaWatcher()` call.\n\n**Check**: Backend `tsc --noEmit` вЂ” pass. `pnpm lint` вЂ” pass. Pre-existing typecheck error in `CloseCallRoundPage.tsx` (not related to changes).\n\n## Iteration 2 вЂ” 2026-03-19T18:48:15Z вЂ” OK\n- **Log**: iteration-002.log\n\n## Iteration 3 вЂ” Lord of the RNGs write paths\n\n**Item**: [engine] Lord of the RNGs write paths вЂ” win + loss rows at settlement\n\n**Changes**:\n- `services/backend/src/worker/settle-tx.ts`: In `settleLordRound()`, after `settle_confirmed` operator event, added user transaction writes. One `win` row for the winner (amountLamports = payoutAmount, txSig) and one `loss` row per losing entry from `roundData.entries` (amountLamports = entry's individual amount, txSig). Game = \"lord\". Uses `Promise.all` for parallel writes. ON CONFLICT DO NOTHING handles duplicate entries for same player.\n\n**Check**: `pnpm lint` вЂ” pass. `pnpm typecheck` вЂ” backend passes. Pre-existing platform typecheck error in `CloseCallRoundPage.tsx` (not related to changes).\n\n## Iteration 3 вЂ” 2026-03-19T18:50:30Z вЂ” OK\n- **Log**: iteration-003.log\n\n## Iteration 4 вЂ” Close Call write paths\n\n**Item**: [engine] Close Call write paths вЂ” join + outcome rows per entry at settlement\n\n**Changes**:\n- `services/backend/src/worker/closecall-clock.ts`: In `settleRound()`, after the DB settlement update, added user transaction writes using raw `sql` tagged template (consistent with file's existing pattern вЂ” this worker receives `sql` not the `Db` object). For each entry in `greenEntries` and `redEntries`: (a) one `join` row (amount = entry.amountLamports), (b) one outcome row вЂ” `win` with payout = `floor((entryAmount / sidePool) * netPool)` if on winning side, `loss` with original amount if on losing side, or `refund` with original amount if `isRefund`. Game = \"closecall\", match_id = round_id (minute timestamp). All writes use `ON CONFLICT DO NOTHING` for idempotency. Inserts are parallelized via `Promise.all`.\n\n**Check**: `pnpm lint` вЂ” pass. `pnpm typecheck` вЂ” backend passes. Pre-existing platform typecheck error in `CloseCallRoundPage.tsx` (not related to changes).\n\n## Iteration 4 вЂ” 2026-03-19T18:53:47Z вЂ” OK\n- **Log**: iteration-004.log\n\n## Iteration 5 вЂ” API route GET /profile/transactions\n\n**Item**: [engine] API route `GET /profile/transactions`\n\n**Changes**:\n- `services/backend/src/middleware/jwt-auth.ts`: Added `requireAllMethods?: boolean` config option. When true, JWT verification applies to all HTTP methods (not just POST). Backward compatible вЂ” defaults to false.\n- Created `services/backend/src/routes/profile.ts`: New route handler with `GET /transactions`. Extracts wallet from JWT `c.get(\"wallet\")`. Supports query params: `cursor` (pagination by id), `limit` (default 20, max 50), `game` (accepts both DB names like `lord` and frontend names like `lord-of-rngs`). Maps response: `game` в†’ frontend names (`lord` в†’ `lord-of-rngs`, `closecall` в†’ `close-call`), `amountLamports` as string, `matchId` camelCase, `createdAt` ISO string. Returns `{ transactions: [...], nextCursor: string | null }`.\n- `services/backend/src/index.ts`: Registered profile routes at `/profile` with `requireAllMethods: true` JWT middleware.\n\n**Check**: `pnpm lint` вЂ” pass. Backend `tsc --noEmit` вЂ” pass. Pre-existing platform typecheck error in `CloseCallRoundPage.tsx` (not related).\n\n## Iteration 5 вЂ” 2026-03-19T18:57:43Z вЂ” OK\n- **Log**: iteration-005.log\n\n## Iteration 6 вЂ” SOL/USD price endpoint\n\n**Item**: [engine] SOL/USD price endpoint вЂ” `GET /price/sol-usd`\n\n**Changes**:\n- Created `services/backend/src/routes/price.ts`: New route handler with `GET /sol-usd`. Uses `@pythnetwork/hermes-client` HermesClient to fetch SOL/USD price (feed ID `0xef0d8b...`). In-memory cache with 60s TTL вЂ” returns stale cache on fetch error (graceful degradation). Response: `{ price: number, expo: number, updatedAt: string }`. Returns 503 if no price available at all.\n- `services/backend/src/index.ts`: Imported `createPriceRoutes`, registered at `/price` with no auth middleware (public endpoint).\n\n**Check**: `pnpm lint` вЂ” pass (0 errors). Backend `tsc --noEmit` вЂ” pass. Pre-existing platform typecheck error in `CloseCallRoundPage.tsx` (not related).\n\n## Iteration 6 вЂ” 2026-03-19T19:05:00Z вЂ” OK\n- **Log**: iteration-006.log\n\n## Iteration 6 вЂ” 2026-03-19T19:00:41Z вЂ” OK\n- **Log**: iteration-006.log\n\n## Iteration 7 вЂ” Wire ProfileTransactions to real API\n\n**Item**: [frontend] Wire `ProfileTransactions` to real API\n\n**Changes**:\n- `apps/platform/src/features/player-profile/types.ts`: Updated `ProfileTransaction` type to match API shape вЂ” added `TransactionEvent` type (`join`/`win`/`loss`/`refund`), replaced `outcome`/`wagerAmount`/`payoutAmount`/`netResult`/`timestamp` fields with `event`/`amountLamports`/`txSig`/`createdAt`.\n- `apps/platform/src/features/player-profile/utils/mock-simulation.ts`: Updated `recordTransaction()` to produce new-shaped `ProfileTransaction` objects (join + outcome rows per game result, amounts in lamports-as-string).\n- Created `apps/platform/src/features/player-profile/hooks/useTransactions.ts`: New hook that fetches from `GET /profile/transactions` with JWT Bearer auth, supports cursor-based pagination and game filter, handles abort cleanup.\n- `apps/platform/src/features/player-profile/components/ProfileTransactions.tsx`: Rewrote to use `useTransactions` hook. Removed mock `getTransactions` import. New columns: Time, Game (linked to match page), Event (color-coded), Amount (SOL). Added loading skeleton (shimmer animation), empty state, and \"Load more\" button for pagination.\n- `apps/platform/src/features/player-profile/components/ProfilePage.tsx`: Removed `address` prop from `<ProfileTransactions>` (now uses JWT, not address).\n- `apps/platform/src/features/player-profile/hooks/index.ts`: Exported `useTransactions` hook.\n- `apps/platform/src/features/player-profile/index.ts`: Exported `TransactionEvent` type.\n- `apps/platform/src/index.css`: Replaced old outcome/net styles with event type styles (win=green, loss=pink, join=muted, refund=blue), added match link hover, loading skeleton shimmer animation, load more button styles.\n\n**Check**: `pnpm lint` вЂ” 0 errors (145 pre-existing warnings). `tsc --noEmit` вЂ” only pre-existing CloseCallRoundPage error (not related).\n\n## Iteration 7 вЂ” 2026-03-19T19:09:37Z вЂ” OK\n- **Log**: iteration-007.log\n\n## Iteration 8 вЂ” SOL amount display with USD estimate\n\n**Item**: [frontend] SOL amount display with USD estimate\n\n**Changes**:\n- Created `apps/platform/src/features/player-profile/hooks/useSolPrice.ts`: New hook that fetches `GET /price/sol-usd` from backend, caches price in React state, refreshes every 60s. Returns `number | null` вЂ” null when unavailable (graceful degradation).\n- `apps/platform/src/features/player-profile/hooks/index.ts`: Exported `useSolPrice` hook.\n- `apps/platform/src/features/player-profile/components/ProfileTransactions.tsx`: Updated `formatSol()` to accept optional `solUsdPrice` param. When price is available, displays `\"0.50 SOL (~$75.00)\"`. When null, shows SOL only. Added `useSolPrice()` call in component, passed to all amount cells.\n\n**Check**: `pnpm lint` вЂ” 0 errors. `pnpm typecheck` вЂ” only pre-existing CloseCallRoundPage error (not related).\n\n## Iteration 8 вЂ” 2026-03-19T19:11:52Z вЂ” OK\n- **Log**: iteration-008.log\n\n","numLines":124,"startLine":1,"totalLines":124}}}
