{"type":"user","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"tool_use_id":"toolu_013Pmzpya56sxen9GEbE9TSS","type":"tool_result","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Perfect! Now I have everything. Let me compile a comprehensive summary document for you.\n\n## Complete Player Profile Feature Documentation\n\nHere's the complete breakdown of the player-profile feature directory for implementing E2E tests:\n\n### **File Structure Overview**\n\n```\nsrc/features/player-profile/\nв”њв”Ђв”Ђ components/\nв”‚   в”њв”Ђв”Ђ ProfileTransactions.tsx      (Main component being tested)\nв”‚   в”њв”Ђв”Ђ ProfilePage.tsx              (Page layout/router)\nв”‚   в”њв”Ђв”Ђ ProfileStats.tsx             (Stats tab content)\nв”‚   в”њв”Ђв”Ђ ProfileSettings.tsx           (Settings tab content)\nв”‚   в”њв”Ђв”Ђ PlayerAvatar.tsx\nв”‚   в”њв”Ђв”Ђ PlayerAvatarCompact.tsx\nв”‚   в”њв”Ђв”Ђ LevelProgressBar.tsx\nв”‚   в”њв”Ђв”Ђ MiniProfileModal.tsx\nв”‚   в”њв”Ђв”Ђ ProfileLoot.tsx\nв”‚   в”њв”Ђв”Ђ AvatarSelectorModal.tsx\nв”‚   в”њв”Ђв”Ђ AvatarSelector.tsx\nв”‚   в””в”Ђв”Ђ index.ts                     (Component exports)\nв”њв”Ђв”Ђ context/\nв”‚   в””в”Ђв”Ђ PlayerProfileContext.tsx     (Global state management)\nв”њв”Ђв”Ђ hooks/\nв”‚   в”њв”Ђв”Ђ useTransactions.ts           (Data fetching hook)\nв”‚   в”њв”Ђв”Ђ useSolPrice.ts               (Price hook)\nв”‚   в””в”Ђв”Ђ index.ts                     (Hook exports)\nв”њв”Ђв”Ђ utils/\nв”‚   в”њв”Ђв”Ђ mock-simulation.ts           (Mock data generation & store)\nв”‚   в”њв”Ђв”Ђ xp-calculator.ts             (XP formulas)\nв”‚   в””в”Ђв”Ђ profile-event-bus.ts         (Event emitter)\nв”њв”Ђв”Ђ types.ts                         (Type definitions)\nв”њв”Ђв”Ђ index.ts                         (Public API)\nв””в”Ђв”Ђ assets/avatars/\n```\n\n---\n\n### **Key Files For E2E Testing**\n\n#### **1. ProfileTransactions.tsx** (Main Component)\n**Location:** `/workspaces/rng-utopia/sources/rng-utopia/apps/platform/src/features/player-profile/components/ProfileTransactions.tsx`\n\n**Exports:** `ProfileTransactions` component\n**Dependencies:**\n- `useTransactions()` hook вЂ” fetches real transaction data\n- `useSolPrice()` hook вЂ” fetches SOL/USD price\n- `GAME_NAMES` from types\n\n**Key Features:**\n- Displays paginated table of transactions with columns: Time, Game, Event, Amount\n- Loading skeleton (5 rows)\n- Empty state when no transactions\n- Load more button for pagination (when `nextCursor` exists)\n- Event types: \"join\", \"win\", \"loss\", \"refund\"\n- Formats amounts as SOL with optional USD estimate\n- Formats timestamps as relative time (\"Just now\", \"5m ago\", \"2h ago\", etc.)\n- Deep links to game rounds: `/{gameId}/{matchId}`\n\n**Test Scenarios:**\n1. Loading state вЂ” show skeleton rows\n2. Empty state вЂ” no transactions yet\n3. Table with transactions вЂ” rows render correctly\n4. Load more button вЂ” enabled when nextCursor exists, disabled when loading\n5. Amount formatting вЂ” SOL + USD estimate when price available\n6. Time formatting вЂ” relative times\n\n---\n\n#### **2. ProfilePage.tsx** (Page Layout & Container)\n**Location:** `/workspaces/rng-utopia/sources/rng-utopia/apps/platform/src/features/player-profile/components/ProfilePage.tsx`\n\n**Route:** `/profile` (from App.tsx line 379)\n\n**Key Features:**\n- Header section with avatar (clickable to open avatar selector modal), username editing, level progress bar, and RNG Buff indicator\n- Three tabs: Statistics, Transactions, Settings\n- Tab content renders based on active tab\n- Username editing inline with validation (3-20 chars, alphanumeric + underscores)\n- Buff timer countdown display\n- Avatar modal for changing avatar\n- Edit/save/cancel buttons with icons\n- Loading state when profile not loaded\n- Wallet connection prompt when no profile\n\n**Test Scenarios:**\n1. Profile loading state\n2. Wallet not connected вЂ” show connect prompt\n3. Header rendering вЂ” avatar, name, level progress\n4. Tab switching вЂ” stats в†’ transactions в†’ settings\n5. Username editing вЂ” input, validation, save/cancel\n6. Avatar selector modal вЂ” open/close\n7. Buff indicator вЂ” timer countdown (if has RNG Buff)\n\n---\n\n#### **3. types.ts** (Type Definitions)\n**Location:** `/workspaces/rng-utopia/sources/rng-utopia/apps/platform/src/features/player-profile/types.ts`\n\n**Key Types:**\n```typescript\n// Transaction history\ninterface ProfileTransaction {\n  id: string;\n  gameId: GameId;  // \"coinflip\" | \"lord-of-rngs\" | \"crypto-crash\" | \"close-call\" | \"game-of-trades\"\n  matchId: string;\n  event: TransactionEvent;  // \"join\" | \"win\" | \"loss\" | \"refund\"\n  amountLamports: string;\n  txSig: string | null;\n  createdAt: string;  // ISO date\n}\n\n// Player profile\ninterface PlayerProfile {\n  address: string;\n  username: string | null;\n  avatarId: AvatarId;\n  level: number;\n  currentXP: number;\n  totalXP: number;\n  discordUsername: string | null;\n  twitterHandle: string | null;\n  stats: PlayerStats;\n  unclaimedLoot: LootItem[];\n  createdAt: number;\n  lastActiveAt: number;\n}\n\n// Game types\ntype GameId = \"coinflip\" | \"lord-of-rngs\" | \"crypto-crash\" | \"close-call\" | \"game-of-trades\";\nconst GAME_NAMES: Record<GameId, string> = { ... }\n```\n\n---\n\n#### **4. hooks/useTransactions.ts** (Data Fetching)\n**Location:** `/workspaces/rng-utopia/sources/rng-utopia/apps/platform/src/features/player-profile/hooks/useTransactions.ts`\n\n**Hook Signature:**\n```typescript\nfunction useTransactions(game?: string) {\n  return {\n    transactions: Transaction[],     // Array of fetched transactions\n    loading: boolean,                // Initial load state\n    loadingMore: boolean,            // Load more button state\n    nextCursor: string | null,       // Pagination cursor\n    loadMore: () => void,            // Load next page\n    error: string | null\n  }\n}\n```\n\n**API Endpoint:** `GET ${BACKEND_URL}/profile/transactions?limit=20&cursor=...&game=...`\n\n**Auth:** Bearer JWT token from `getAccessToken()`\n\n**Backend URL:** `VITE_FAIRNESS_BACKEND_URL` (defaults to `http://127.0.0.1:3100`)\n\n**Pagination:** Cursor-based, limit 20 per page\n\n**Test Scenarios:**\n1. No auth token вЂ” returns empty transactions\n2. Fetch initial page вЂ” sets transactions, nextCursor\n3. Load more вЂ” appends to transactions array\n4. Error handling вЂ” network failures, HTTP errors\n5. Abort in-flight requests on dependency change\n\n---\n\n#### **5. hooks/useSolPrice.ts** (Price Fetching)\n**Location:** `/workspaces/rng-utopia/sources/rng-utopia/apps/platform/src/features/player-profile/hooks/useSolPrice.ts`\n\n**Hook Signature:**\n```typescript\nfunction useSolPrice(): number | null {\n  // Returns SOL/USD price or null if unavailable\n}\n```\n\n**API Endpoint:** `GET ${BACKEND_URL}/price/sol-usd`\n\n**Expected Response:** `{ price: number }`\n\n**Refresh Interval:** 60 seconds\n\n**Graceful Degradation:** Errors are swallowed; keeps previous price or null\n\n**Test Scenarios:**\n1. Initial fetch вЂ” returns price\n2. Periodic refresh вЂ” updates every 60s\n3. API error вЂ” gracefully degrades to null\n4. Cleanup вЂ” interval cleared on unmount\n\n---\n\n#### **6. utils/mock-simulation.ts** (In-Memory Store)\n**Location:** `/workspaces/rng-utopia/sources/rng-utopia/apps/platform/src/features/player-profile/utils/mock-simulation.ts`\n\n**Key Functions:**\n```typescript\n// Profile CRUD\ngetProfile(address: string): PlayerProfile | null\ngetOrCreateProfile(address: string, forceLevel?: number): PlayerProfile\nupdateProfile(address: string, updates: Partial<...>): PlayerProfile\nupdateUsername(address: string, username: string | null): PlayerProfile\nupdateAvatar(address: string, avatarId: AvatarId): PlayerProfile\n\n// Game results & stats\nrecordGameResult(event: GameResultEvent): void  // Updates profile stats & XP\ngetTransactions(address: string, limit = 50): ProfileTransaction[]\n\n// Loot system\naddLoot(address: string, source, amount, description, gameId?, matchId?, expiresAt?): void\nclaimLoot(address: string, lootId: string): number\nclaimAllLoot(address: string): number\n\n// Subscriptions\nsubscribeToProfiles(callback): () => void  // Returns unsubscribe function\n\n// Display helpers\ngetDisplayName(address: string): string\ngetAvatarId(address: string): AvatarId\ntruncateAddress(address: string): string\n```\n\n**Mock Data Generation:**\n- Random usernames: `${ADJECTIVE}${NOUN}${number}` (e.g., \"CosmicWhale42\")\n- Random levels: weighted distribution (50% lv1-15, 30% lv16-40, 15% lv41-70, 5% lv71-100)\n- Random avatars: pick unlocked avatar for given level\n- Random stats: based on level\n\n**Test Scenarios:**\n1. Create/retrieve profiles with forced levels\n2. Update profile fields\n3. Record game results в†’ update stats/XP\n4. Transaction recording (join + outcome events)\n5. Loot claiming\n6. Profile update subscriptions\n\n---\n\n#### **7. utils/xp-calculator.ts** (XP Formulas)\n**Location:** `/workspaces/rng-utopia/sources/rng-utopia/apps/platform/src/features/player-profile/utils/xp-calculator.ts`\n\n**Key Functions:**\n```typescript\ngetXPForLevel(level: number): number\n  // Formula: 50 * levelВІ + 50 * level\n  // Level 1: 100 XP, Level 5: 1,500 XP, Level 100: 505,000 XP\n\ngetLevelFromXP(totalXP: number): number\n  // Reverse formula using quadratic equation\n\ngetXPProgress(totalXP: number): XPProgress\n  // Returns: level, currentXP, xpForNextLevel, xpNeededForNext, progressPercent, isMaxLevel\n\ncalculateGameXP(wagerAmount: number, isWin: boolean): number\n  // Base: 100 XP per SOL wagered + 50% bonus if win\n\ngetBorderStyleFromLevel(level: number): BorderStyle\n  // Level 5: iron, 10: silver, 15: gold, 20: platinum, 25: diamond\n```\n\n---\n\n#### **8. utils/profile-event-bus.ts** (Cross-Feature Events)\n**Location:** `/workspaces/rng-utopia/sources/rng-utopia/apps/platform/src/features/player-profile/utils/profile-event-bus.ts`\n\n**Event Bus Pattern:**\n```typescript\nprofileEventBus.emit(event: GameResultEvent): void\nprofileEventBus.subscribe(callback): () => void  // Returns unsubscribe\n```\n\n**Helper Emitters:**\n```typescript\nemitGameResult(gameId, matchId, playerAddress, wagerAmount, outcome, payoutAmount)\nemitCoinflipResults(matchId, winner, loser, entryAmount, payoutAmount)\nemitLordOfRngsResults(roundId, winner, participants, payoutAmount)\nemitCryptoCrashResults(roundId, results[])\nemitCloseCallResults(roundId, results[])\nemitGameOfTradesResults(roundId, results[])\ncreateGameResultEvent(...): GameResultEvent\n```\n\n---\n\n### **Route Definition**\n\n**Location:** `/workspaces/rng-utopia/sources/rng-utopia/apps/platform/src/App.tsx` line 379\n\n```tsx\n<Route path=\"/profile\" element={<ProfilePage />} />\n```\n\n**Provider Stack:**\n```tsx\n<BrowserRouter>\n  <PriceFeedProvider>\n    <PlayerProfileProvider>\n      <QuestsProvider>\n        <BossRaidProvider>\n          <AppContent />\n        </BossRaidProvider>\n      </QuestsProvider>\n    </PlayerProfileProvider>\n  </PriceFeedProvider>\n</BrowserRouter>\n```\n\n---\n\n### **Component Exports (index.ts)**\n\n**Location:** `/workspaces/rng-utopia/sources/rng-utopia/apps/platform/src/features/player-profile/index.ts`\n\n**Main Exports:**\n- `PlayerProfileProvider`, `usePlayerProfile`, `truncateAddress`\n- `PlayerAvatar`, `PlayerAvatarCompact`, `LevelProgressBar`, `MiniProfileModal`, `ProfilePage`, `AvatarSelector`\n- All types: `AvatarId`, `PlayerProfile`, `ProfileTransaction`, `GameId`, etc.\n- XP utilities: `getXPForLevel`, `getLevelFromXP`, `getXPProgress`, `calculateGameXP`, `getBorderStyleFromLevel`\n- Event emitters: `profileEventBus`, `emitGameResult`, `emitCoinflipResults`, etc.\n- Mock helpers: `getProfile`, `getOrCreateProfile`, `getTransactions`, `getDisplayName`, `getAvatarId`, `addLoot`\n\n---\n\n### **Test Implementation Notes**\n\n**For ProfileTransactions Component:**\n1. Mock `useTransactions()` to control loading, transactions, pagination state\n2. Mock `useSolPrice()` to return fixed price or null\n3. Test table rendering with various transaction lists\n4. Test formatters (time, amount)\n5. Test deep links to `/coinflip/:matchId`, `/lord-of-rngs/:matchId`, etc.\n6. Test load more button behavior\n\n**For ProfilePage:**\n1. Mock `usePlayerProfile()` context\n2. Test tab switching with router context\n3. Test username validation (3-20 chars, alphanumeric + underscore)\n4. Test avatar modal open/close\n5. Test buff timer countdown with real timers\n6. Verify edit/save/cancel button states\n\n**Backend Mocking:**\n- Mock `fetch()` for `/profile/transactions` API\n- Mock `/price/sol-usd` endpoint\n- Set `VITE_FAIRNESS_BACKEND_URL` in test environment\n\n**Auth Mocking:**\n- Mock `getAccessToken()` from `lib/auth-store` to return JWT token or null\n\n---\n\n### **Key Constants**\n\n- **Max username:** 20 characters\n- **Min username:** 3 characters\n- **Username regex:** `/^[a-zA-Z0-9_]+$/`\n- **Avatar unlock levels:** Recruit (1), Mercenary (5), Cadet (10), Knight (20), Champion (30), Paladin (40), Grandmaster (50), Warlord (60), Sovereign (70), Archon (80), Ascendant (90), Cosmic Deity (100)\n- **Border styles:** none (0), iron (5), silver (10), gold (15), platinum (20), diamond (25)\n- **Game names:** Flip You, Jackpot, Crypto Crash, Close Call, Game of Trades\n\n---\n\nThis gives you complete visibility into the feature for implementing comprehensive E2E tests."},{"type":"text","text":"agentId: a513cdf5252edb2b1 (use SendMessage with to: 'a513cdf5252edb2b1' to continue this agent)\n<usage>total_tokens: 68562\ntool_uses: 21\nduration_ms: 52745</usage>"}]}]},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"session_id":"b99e2185-20b1-487e-a0a4-b3fb9a756d45","uuid":"ad84bc1d-55c3-44b1-8713-4f5c105610a0","timestamp":"2026-03-19T19:13:15.450Z","tool_use_result":{"status":"completed","prompt":"Read all files in the player-profile feature directory at sources/rng-utopia/apps/platform/src/features/player-profile/. I need to see:\n1. ProfileTransactions.tsx вЂ” the main component being tested\n2. ProfilePage.tsx вЂ” the page layout\n3. types.ts вЂ” the ProfileTransaction type\n4. hooks/useTransactions.ts вЂ” the data fetching hook\n5. hooks/useSolPrice.ts вЂ” the price hook\n6. utils/mock-simulation.ts вЂ” mock data generation\n7. The index.ts exports\n8. Any route definitions for the profile page\n\nRead each file completely. This is for implementing E2E tests.","agentId":"a513cdf5252edb2b1","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Perfect! Now I have everything. Let me compile a comprehensive summary document for you.\n\n## Complete Player Profile Feature Documentation\n\nHere's the complete breakdown of the player-profile feature directory for implementing E2E tests:\n\n### **File Structure Overview**\n\n```\nsrc/features/player-profile/\nв”њв”Ђв”Ђ components/\nв”‚   в”њв”Ђв”Ђ ProfileTransactions.tsx      (Main component being tested)\nв”‚   в”њв”Ђв”Ђ ProfilePage.tsx              (Page layout/router)\nв”‚   в”њв”Ђв”Ђ ProfileStats.tsx             (Stats tab content)\nв”‚   в”њв”Ђв”Ђ ProfileSettings.tsx           (Settings tab content)\nв”‚   в”њв”Ђв”Ђ PlayerAvatar.tsx\nв”‚   в”њв”Ђв”Ђ PlayerAvatarCompact.tsx\nв”‚   в”њв”Ђв”Ђ LevelProgressBar.tsx\nв”‚   в”њв”Ђв”Ђ MiniProfileModal.tsx\nв”‚   в”њв”Ђв”Ђ ProfileLoot.tsx\nв”‚   в”њв”Ђв”Ђ AvatarSelectorModal.tsx\nв”‚   в”њв”Ђв”Ђ AvatarSelector.tsx\nв”‚   в””в”Ђв”Ђ index.ts                     (Component exports)\nв”њв”Ђв”Ђ context/\nв”‚   в””в”Ђв”Ђ PlayerProfileContext.tsx     (Global state management)\nв”њв”Ђв”Ђ hooks/\nв”‚   в”њв”Ђв”Ђ useTransactions.ts           (Data fetching hook)\nв”‚   в”њв”Ђв”Ђ useSolPrice.ts               (Price hook)\nв”‚   в””в”Ђв”Ђ index.ts                     (Hook exports)\nв”њв”Ђв”Ђ utils/\nв”‚   в”њв”Ђв”Ђ mock-simulation.ts           (Mock data generation & store)\nв”‚   в”њв”Ђв”Ђ xp-calculator.ts             (XP formulas)\nв”‚   в””в”Ђв”Ђ profile-event-bus.ts         (Event emitter)\nв”њв”Ђв”Ђ types.ts                         (Type definitions)\nв”њв”Ђв”Ђ index.ts                         (Public API)\nв””в”Ђв”Ђ assets/avatars/\n```\n\n---\n\n### **Key Files For E2E Testing**\n\n#### **1. ProfileTransactions.tsx** (Main Component)\n**Location:** `/workspaces/rng-utopia/sources/rng-utopia/apps/platform/src/features/player-profile/components/ProfileTransactions.tsx`\n\n**Exports:** `ProfileTransactions` component\n**Dependencies:**\n- `useTransactions()` hook вЂ” fetches real transaction data\n- `useSolPrice()` hook вЂ” fetches SOL/USD price\n- `GAME_NAMES` from types\n\n**Key Features:**\n- Displays paginated table of transactions with columns: Time, Game, Event, Amount\n- Loading skeleton (5 rows)\n- Empty state when no transactions\n- Load more button for pagination (when `nextCursor` exists)\n- Event types: \"join\", \"win\", \"loss\", \"refund\"\n- Formats amounts as SOL with optional USD estimate\n- Formats timestamps as relative time (\"Just now\", \"5m ago\", \"2h ago\", etc.)\n- Deep links to game rounds: `/{gameId}/{matchId}`\n\n**Test Scenarios:**\n1. Loading state вЂ” show skeleton rows\n2. Empty state вЂ” no transactions yet\n3. Table with transactions вЂ” rows render correctly\n4. Load more button вЂ” enabled when nextCursor exists, disabled when loading\n5. Amount formatting вЂ” SOL + USD estimate when price available\n6. Time formatting вЂ” relative times\n\n---\n\n#### **2. ProfilePage.tsx** (Page Layout & Container)\n**Location:** `/workspaces/rng-utopia/sources/rng-utopia/apps/platform/src/features/player-profile/components/ProfilePage.tsx`\n\n**Route:** `/profile` (from App.tsx line 379)\n\n**Key Features:**\n- Header section with avatar (clickable to open avatar selector modal), username editing, level progress bar, and RNG Buff indicator\n- Three tabs: Statistics, Transactions, Settings\n- Tab content renders based on active tab\n- Username editing inline with validation (3-20 chars, alphanumeric + underscores)\n- Buff timer countdown display\n- Avatar modal for changing avatar\n- Edit/save/cancel buttons with icons\n- Loading state when profile not loaded\n- Wallet connection prompt when no profile\n\n**Test Scenarios:**\n1. Profile loading state\n2. Wallet not connected вЂ” show connect prompt\n3. Header rendering вЂ” avatar, name, level progress\n4. Tab switching вЂ” stats в†’ transactions в†’ settings\n5. Username editing вЂ” input, validation, save/cancel\n6. Avatar selector modal вЂ” open/close\n7. Buff indicator вЂ” timer countdown (if has RNG Buff)\n\n---\n\n#### **3. types.ts** (Type Definitions)\n**Location:** `/workspaces/rng-utopia/sources/rng-utopia/apps/platform/src/features/player-profile/types.ts`\n\n**Key Types:**\n```typescript\n// Transaction history\ninterface ProfileTransaction {\n  id: string;\n  gameId: GameId;  // \"coinflip\" | \"lord-of-rngs\" | \"crypto-crash\" | \"close-call\" | \"game-of-trades\"\n  matchId: string;\n  event: TransactionEvent;  // \"join\" | \"win\" | \"loss\" | \"refund\"\n  amountLamports: string;\n  txSig: string | null;\n  createdAt: string;  // ISO date\n}\n\n// Player profile\ninterface PlayerProfile {\n  address: string;\n  username: string | null;\n  avatarId: AvatarId;\n  level: number;\n  currentXP: number;\n  totalXP: number;\n  discordUsername: string | null;\n  twitterHandle: string | null;\n  stats: PlayerStats;\n  unclaimedLoot: LootItem[];\n  createdAt: number;\n  lastActiveAt: number;\n}\n\n// Game types\ntype GameId = \"coinflip\" | \"lord-of-rngs\" | \"crypto-crash\" | \"close-call\" | \"game-of-trades\";\nconst GAME_NAMES: Record<GameId, string> = { ... }\n```\n\n---\n\n#### **4. hooks/useTransactions.ts** (Data Fetching)\n**Location:** `/workspaces/rng-utopia/sources/rng-utopia/apps/platform/src/features/player-profile/hooks/useTransactions.ts`\n\n**Hook Signature:**\n```typescript\nfunction useTransactions(game?: string) {\n  return {\n    transactions: Transaction[],     // Array of fetched transactions\n    loading: boolean,                // Initial load state\n    loadingMore: boolean,            // Load more button state\n    nextCursor: string | null,       // Pagination cursor\n    loadMore: () => void,            // Load next page\n    error: string | null\n  }\n}\n```\n\n**API Endpoint:** `GET ${BACKEND_URL}/profile/transactions?limit=20&cursor=...&game=...`\n\n**Auth:** Bearer JWT token from `getAccessToken()`\n\n**Backend URL:** `VITE_FAIRNESS_BACKEND_URL` (defaults to `http://127.0.0.1:3100`)\n\n**Pagination:** Cursor-based, limit 20 per page\n\n**Test Scenarios:**\n1. No auth token вЂ” returns empty transactions\n2. Fetch initial page вЂ” sets transactions, nextCursor\n3. Load more вЂ” appends to transactions array\n4. Error handling вЂ” network failures, HTTP errors\n5. Abort in-flight requests on dependency change\n\n---\n\n#### **5. hooks/useSolPrice.ts** (Price Fetching)\n**Location:** `/workspaces/rng-utopia/sources/rng-utopia/apps/platform/src/features/player-profile/hooks/useSolPrice.ts`\n\n**Hook Signature:**\n```typescript\nfunction useSolPrice(): number | null {\n  // Returns SOL/USD price or null if unavailable\n}\n```\n\n**API Endpoint:** `GET ${BACKEND_URL}/price/sol-usd`\n\n**Expected Response:** `{ price: number }`\n\n**Refresh Interval:** 60 seconds\n\n**Graceful Degradation:** Errors are swallowed; keeps previous price or null\n\n**Test Scenarios:**\n1. Initial fetch вЂ” returns price\n2. Periodic refresh вЂ” updates every 60s\n3. API error вЂ” gracefully degrades to null\n4. Cleanup вЂ” interval cleared on unmount\n\n---\n\n#### **6. utils/mock-simulation.ts** (In-Memory Store)\n**Location:** `/workspaces/rng-utopia/sources/rng-utopia/apps/platform/src/features/player-profile/utils/mock-simulation.ts`\n\n**Key Functions:**\n```typescript\n// Profile CRUD\ngetProfile(address: string): PlayerProfile | null\ngetOrCreateProfile(address: string, forceLevel?: number): PlayerProfile\nupdateProfile(address: string, updates: Partial<...>): PlayerProfile\nupdateUsername(address: string, username: string | null): PlayerProfile\nupdateAvatar(address: string, avatarId: AvatarId): PlayerProfile\n\n// Game results & stats\nrecordGameResult(event: GameResultEvent): void  // Updates profile stats & XP\ngetTransactions(address: string, limit = 50): ProfileTransaction[]\n\n// Loot system\naddLoot(address: string, source, amount, description, gameId?, matchId?, expiresAt?): void\nclaimLoot(address: string, lootId: string): number\nclaimAllLoot(address: string): number\n\n// Subscriptions\nsubscribeToProfiles(callback): () => void  // Returns unsubscribe function\n\n// Display helpers\ngetDisplayName(address: string): string\ngetAvatarId(address: string): AvatarId\ntruncateAddress(address: string): string\n```\n\n**Mock Data Generation:**\n- Random usernames: `${ADJECTIVE}${NOUN}${number}` (e.g., \"CosmicWhale42\")\n- Random levels: weighted distribution (50% lv1-15, 30% lv16-40, 15% lv41-70, 5% lv71-100)\n- Random avatars: pick unlocked avatar for given level\n- Random stats: based on level\n\n**Test Scenarios:**\n1. Create/retrieve profiles with forced levels\n2. Update profile fields\n3. Record game results в†’ update stats/XP\n4. Transaction recording (join + outcome events)\n5. Loot claiming\n6. Profile update subscriptions\n\n---\n\n#### **7. utils/xp-calculator.ts** (XP Formulas)\n**Location:** `/workspaces/rng-utopia/sources/rng-utopia/apps/platform/src/features/player-profile/utils/xp-calculator.ts`\n\n**Key Functions:**\n```typescript\ngetXPForLevel(level: number): number\n  // Formula: 50 * levelВІ + 50 * level\n  // Level 1: 100 XP, Level 5: 1,500 XP, Level 100: 505,000 XP\n\ngetLevelFromXP(totalXP: number): number\n  // Reverse formula using quadratic equation\n\ngetXPProgress(totalXP: number): XPProgress\n  // Returns: level, currentXP, xpForNextLevel, xpNeededForNext, progressPercent, isMaxLevel\n\ncalculateGameXP(wagerAmount: number, isWin: boolean): number\n  // Base: 100 XP per SOL wagered + 50% bonus if win\n\ngetBorderStyleFromLevel(level: number): BorderStyle\n  // Level 5: iron, 10: silver, 15: gold, 20: platinum, 25: diamond\n```\n\n---\n\n#### **8. utils/profile-event-bus.ts** (Cross-Feature Events)\n**Location:** `/workspaces/rng-utopia/sources/rng-utopia/apps/platform/src/features/player-profile/utils/profile-event-bus.ts`\n\n**Event Bus Pattern:**\n```typescript\nprofileEventBus.emit(event: GameResultEvent): void\nprofileEventBus.subscribe(callback): () => void  // Returns unsubscribe\n```\n\n**Helper Emitters:**\n```typescript\nemitGameResult(gameId, matchId, playerAddress, wagerAmount, outcome, payoutAmount)\nemitCoinflipResults(matchId, winner, loser, entryAmount, payoutAmount)\nemitLordOfRngsResults(roundId, winner, participants, payoutAmount)\nemitCryptoCrashResults(roundId, results[])\nemitCloseCallResults(roundId, results[])\nemitGameOfTradesResults(roundId, results[])\ncreateGameResultEvent(...): GameResultEvent\n```\n\n---\n\n### **Route Definition**\n\n**Location:** `/workspaces/rng-utopia/sources/rng-utopia/apps/platform/src/App.tsx` line 379\n\n```tsx\n<Route path=\"/profile\" element={<ProfilePage />} />\n```\n\n**Provider Stack:**\n```tsx\n<BrowserRouter>\n  <PriceFeedProvider>\n    <PlayerProfileProvider>\n      <QuestsProvider>\n        <BossRaidProvider>\n          <AppContent />\n        </BossRaidProvider>\n      </QuestsProvider>\n    </PlayerProfileProvider>\n  </PriceFeedProvider>\n</BrowserRouter>\n```\n\n---\n\n### **Component Exports (index.ts)**\n\n**Location:** `/workspaces/rng-utopia/sources/rng-utopia/apps/platform/src/features/player-profile/index.ts`\n\n**Main Exports:**\n- `PlayerProfileProvider`, `usePlayerProfile`, `truncateAddress`\n- `PlayerAvatar`, `PlayerAvatarCompact`, `LevelProgressBar`, `MiniProfileModal`, `ProfilePage`, `AvatarSelector`\n- All types: `AvatarId`, `PlayerProfile`, `ProfileTransaction`, `GameId`, etc.\n- XP utilities: `getXPForLevel`, `getLevelFromXP`, `getXPProgress`, `calculateGameXP`, `getBorderStyleFromLevel`\n- Event emitters: `profileEventBus`, `emitGameResult`, `emitCoinflipResults`, etc.\n- Mock helpers: `getProfile`, `getOrCreateProfile`, `getTransactions`, `getDisplayName`, `getAvatarId`, `addLoot`\n\n---\n\n### **Test Implementation Notes**\n\n**For ProfileTransactions Component:**\n1. Mock `useTransactions()` to control loading, transactions, pagination state\n2. Mock `useSolPrice()` to return fixed price or null\n3. Test table rendering with various transaction lists\n4. Test formatters (time, amount)\n5. Test deep links to `/coinflip/:matchId`, `/lord-of-rngs/:matchId`, etc.\n6. Test load more button behavior\n\n**For ProfilePage:**\n1. Mock `usePlayerProfile()` context\n2. Test tab switching with router context\n3. Test username validation (3-20 chars, alphanumeric + underscore)\n4. Test avatar modal open/close\n5. Test buff timer countdown with real timers\n6. Verify edit/save/cancel button states\n\n**Backend Mocking:**\n- Mock `fetch()` for `/profile/transactions` API\n- Mock `/price/sol-usd` endpoint\n- Set `VITE_FAIRNESS_BACKEND_URL` in test environment\n\n**Auth Mocking:**\n- Mock `getAccessToken()` from `lib/auth-store` to return JWT token or null\n\n---\n\n### **Key Constants**\n\n- **Max username:** 20 characters\n- **Min username:** 3 characters\n- **Username regex:** `/^[a-zA-Z0-9_]+$/`\n- **Avatar unlock levels:** Recruit (1), Mercenary (5), Cadet (10), Knight (20), Champion (30), Paladin (40), Grandmaster (50), Warlord (60), Sovereign (70), Archon (80), Ascendant (90), Cosmic Deity (100)\n- **Border styles:** none (0), iron (5), silver (10), gold (15), platinum (20), diamond (25)\n- **Game names:** Flip You, Jackpot, Crypto Crash, Close Call, Game of Trades\n\n---\n\nThis gives you complete visibility into the feature for implementing comprehensive E2E tests."}],"totalDurationMs":52745,"totalTokens":68562,"totalToolUseCount":21,"usage":{"input_tokens":5,"cache_creation_input_tokens":4412,"cache_read_input_tokens":60298,"output_tokens":3847,"server_tool_use":{"web_search_requests":0,"web_fetch_requests":0},"se