avigateToCoinflip, createMatch, joinMatch, etc.)\nв”‚       в”њв”Ђв”Ђ on-chain.ts      # RPC assertion helpers (PDA derivation, fee validation, match state)\nв”‚       в”њв”Ђв”Ђ localnet-setup.ts # Config initialization (coinflip, platform, lord configs)\nв”‚       в””в”Ђв”Ђ lord-page-objects.ts\nв”њв”Ђв”Ђ devnet/                  # Devnet E2E tests\nв”‚   в”њв”Ђв”Ђ fixtures.ts          # Same dual-player fixture, using devnet RPC\nв”‚   в”њв”Ђв”Ђ smoke.spec.ts\nв”‚   в”њв”Ђв”Ђ lifecycle.spec.ts\nв”‚   в”њв”Ђв”Ђ lord-lifecycle.spec.ts\nв”‚   в”њв”Ђв”Ђ closecall-lifecycle.spec.ts\nв”‚   в”њв”Ђв”Ђ deeplink.spec.ts\nв”‚   в””в”Ђв”Ђ helpers/\nв”‚       в”њв”Ђв”Ђ env.ts           # Devnet env validation (RPC URL, program IDs)\nв”‚       в”њв”Ђв”Ђ wallets.ts       # Same deterministic keypairs\nв”‚       в”њв”Ђв”Ђ tx-utils.ts\nв”‚       в”њв”Ђв”Ђ vrf-polling.ts\nв”‚       в”њв”Ђв”Ђ retry.ts\nв”‚       в””в”Ђв”Ђ [cleanup/fallback helpers]\nв”њв”Ђв”Ђ visual/                  # Visual regression tests\nв”‚   в”њв”Ђв”Ђ routes.spec.ts       # Route baseline snapshots (home, coinflip, lord, etc.)\nв”‚   в”њв”Ђв”Ђ states.spec.ts       # UI state variants (disconnected, connected, error toasts)\nв”‚   в””в”Ђв”Ђ __snapshots__/       # Baseline images\nв”њв”Ђв”Ђ real/\nв”‚   в””в”Ђв”Ђ startup.spec.ts      # Real app startup test\n```\n\n---\n\n### 2. **Framework & Key Technologies**\n\n| Aspect | Details |\n|--------|---------|\n| **Framework** | Playwright (`@playwright/test` v1.58.2) |\n| **Test Modes** | Visual regression, local integration, devnet integration |\n| **Fixture Pattern** | Extended base Playwright test with custom fixtures |\n| **Auth/Wallet** | Injected deterministic keypair seed via `addInitScript` |\n| **Mock Mode** | `VITE_MOCK_MODE=true` for visual tests; `false` for integration tests |\n| **On-Chain SDK** | Anchor client (`@rng-utopia/anchor-client`) for RPC queries |\n\n---\n\n### 3. **How Existing Local E2E Tests Work**\n\n#### **Fixtures (local/fixtures.ts)**\n- Extends Playwright's base test with `DualPlayerFixtures`\n- Creates **two isolated browser contexts** (Player A and B) with separate storage/cookies\n- Each context gets a **deterministic keypair seed** injected via `addInitScript` before the page loads\n  - Player A seed: `0xaa` repeated (32 bytes)\n  - Player B seed: `0xbb` repeated (32 bytes)\n  - Seed passed as `window.__TEST_WALLET_SEED__` в†’ picked up by `TestWalletProvider`\n- Provides:\n  - `playerAPage`, `playerBPage` вЂ” isolated page instances\n  - `playerAKeypair`, `playerBKeypair` вЂ” Keypair objects for RPC signing\n  - `connection` вЂ” shared `Connection` to local RPC (`http://127.0.0.1:8899`)\n\n#### **Test Pattern (local/03-lifecycle.spec.ts example)**\n```typescript\ntest(\"coinflip full lifecycle\", async ({ playerAPage, playerBPage, connection }) => {\n  // 1. Player A creates a match\n  await po.navigateToCoinflip(playerAPage);\n  await po.createMatch(playerAPage, \"iron\", \"heads\"); // Wager amount, side\n\n  // 2. On-chain assertion: verify PDA state\n  const { matchPda } = await assertMatchCreated(connection, PLAYER_A.publicKey, SIDE_HEADS);\n\n  // 3. Player B joins\n  await po.navigateToCoinflip(playerBPage);\n  await po.waitForLobbyMatch(playerBPage);\n  await po.joinMatch(playerBPage);\n\n  // 4. Both wait for backend settlement\n  const [resultA, resultB] = await Promise.all([\n    po.waitForResult(playerAPage, 30_000),\n    po.waitForResult(playerBPage, 30_000),\n  ]);\n\n  // 5. Assertions: results complementary, match closed, treasury fee received\n  expect(resultA).not.toBe(resultB);\n  await assertMatchClosed(connection, matchPda);\n  await assertTreasuryFee(connection, treasury, treasuryBefore, ENTRY_AMOUNT);\n});\n```\n\n---\n\n### 4. **Mock Mode & Auth Handling**\n\n#### **Visual Tests (fixtures.ts + visual/*.spec.ts)**\n- `VITE_MOCK_MODE=true` вЂ” entire backend mocked, no real RPC calls\n- **Deterministic PRNG**: `Math.random()` seeded with 42 (Mulberry32 algorithm)\n- **Frozen Date**: `Date.now()` = 2026-01-01T00:00:00Z\n- **Seeded crypto.getRandomValues** в†’ deterministic wallet generation on connect\n- **Expected noise patterns** filtered:\n  - 401/403 (mock auth attempts)\n  - 429 (rate limits)\n  - Failed fetch attempts\n- **Animation freeze**: CSS + SVG SMIL paused to ensure stable snapshots\n\n#### **Local & Devnet Tests (real wallet mode)**\n- `VITE_MOCK_MODE=false`, `VITE_TEST_WALLET=true`\n- Seed injected **before page render** в†’ `TestWalletProvider` builds Keypair deterministically\n- No JWT tokens вЂ” wallet signs transactions directly\n- Console error tracking: filter favicon + common noise, fail test on real errors\n\n---\n\n### 5. **Test Execution Scripts**\n\n#### **Package.json scripts**\n```bash\npnpm test:visual              # Visual regression (runs via playwright.config.ts)\npnpm test:visual:update       # Update baselines\npnpm test:e2e:local           # Local validator E2E (bash script orchestration)\npnpm test:e2e:devnet          # Devnet E2E\npnpm test:real                # Real app startup (playwright.real.config.ts)\n```\n\n#### **Local E2E Flow (run-e2e-local.sh)**\n1. Start solana-test-validator + deploy programs\n2. Airdrop SOL to test players\n3. Start PostgreSQL\n4. Run backend migrations\n5. Start fairness backend server on port 3100\n6. Start Vite dev server on port 3002 with test wallet enabled\n7. Run Playwright tests (playwright.local.config.ts)\n8. Cleanup: kill backend, stop validator\n\n---\n\n### 6. **Fixtures & Helpers**\n\n#### **Fixture Files**\n| File | Purpose |\n|------|---------|\n| `fixtures.ts` (root) | `stablePage` вЂ” visual test fixture with deterministic rendering |\n| `local/fixtures.ts` | `playerAPage`, `playerBPage`, dual browser contexts |\n| `devnet/fixtures.ts` | Same as local, but connects to devnet RPC + validates env |\n\n#### **Page Objects (local/helpers/page-objects.ts)**\nCSS-class-based selectors matching actual component markup:\n- **Navigation**: `navigateToCoinflip(page)`\n- **Actions**: `createMatch(page, amount, side)`, `joinMatch(page)`, `cancelMatch(page)`, `claimOrSettle(page)`\n- **Wait primitives**: `waitForPhaseLabel(page, label)`, `waitForResult(page)`, `waitForResultOrLobby(page)`\n- **Assertions**: `assertErrorToast(page)`, `assertNoErrorToast(page)`, `assertLobbyEmpty(page)`\n- **Balance helpers**: `getSolBalance(page, address, rpcUrl)`\n\n#### **On-Chain Helpers (local/helpers/on-chain.ts)**\n- **PDA derivation**: `getMatchPda(creator, matchId)`, `getConfigPda()`, `getLordRoundPda(matchId)`\n- **Fetch helpers**: `fetchMatch(connection, matchPda)`, `fetchLordRound(connection, roundPda)`\n- **Assertions**: \n  - `assertMatchCreated(connection, creator, expectedSide)` вЂ” uses memcmp-based search\n  - `assertMatchClosed(connection, matchPda)` вЂ” verifies account is closed\n  - `assertTreasuryFee(connection, treasury, balanceBefore, entryAmount)` вЂ” validates 3% fee\n  - `calculateExpectedFee(entryAmount)` вЂ” mirrors on-chain fee calculation\n- **Program instances**: `getCoinflipProgram(connection)`, `getLordProgram(connection)`\n\n#### **Wallet Helpers (local/helpers/wallets.ts)**\n- **Deterministic keypairs**:\n  - `PLAYER_A` = `Keypair.fromSeed(0xaa...)` \n  - `PLAYER_B` = `Keypair.fromSeed(0xbb...)`\n- **Airdrop**: `fundWallet(connection, publicKey, solAmount)`, `fundTestWallets()`\n- **Config**: `LOCAL_RPC_URL = http://127.0.0.1:8899`\n\n#### **Localnet Setup (local/helpers/localnet-setup.ts)**\n- **Deterministic admin/treasury keypairs**:\n  - `ADMIN` = `Keypair.fromSeed(0xdd...)`\n  - `TREASURY` = `Keypair.fromSeed(0xcc...)`\n- **Initialization**: `initializeLocalnet()` вЂ” idempotent config PDA setup for:\n  - Coinflip config (authority + treasury)\n  - Platform config (authority + treasury)\n  - Lord of RNGs config (authority + treasury)\n- Helper: `fundIfNeeded(connection, pubkey, solAmount)`\n\n---\n\n### 7. **Visual Tests (visual/*.spec.ts)**\n\n**Two main suites:**\n\n1. **routes.spec.ts** вЂ” baseline snapshots for each route:\n   - Home, coinflip, lord-of-rngs, close-call, crash, game-of-trades, profile, quests, loot, fairness, leaderboard, 404\n\n2. **states.spec.ts** вЂ” UI state variants:\n   - Wallet disconnected / connected\n   - Error toast positioning\n   - Page-specific states (lobby в†’ round view в†’ back to lobby)\n   - Avatar SVG rendering (В±0.03 max diff for sub-pixel variance)\n\n**Fixture enhancements in visual tests:**\n- Clear localStorage to ensure clean state\n- Re-inject animation freeze CSS after wallet connect (if needed)\n- Use `stablePage.evaluate()` for inline JS (e.g., inject error toast)\n- 300ms settle time before screenshot\n\n---\n\n### 8. **Playwright Configs**\n\n| Config | Env Vars | Fixture Match | Purpose |\n|--------|----------|---------------|---------|\n| `playwright.config.ts` | `VITE_MOCK_MODE=true` | `visual/**/*.spec.ts` | Visual regression, auto-starts Vite |\n| `playwright.local.config.ts` | `VITE_TEST_WALLET=true`, `VITE_MOCK_MODE=false` | `local/**/*.spec.ts` | Local validator integration |\n| `playwright.devnet.config.ts` | `VITE_TEST_WALLET=true`, devnet env vars | `devnet/**/*.spec.ts` | Devnet integration, 300s timeout |\n| `playwright.real.config.ts` | (default real app) | `real/**/*.spec.ts` | Real app startup verification |\n\nKey settings:\n- **Parallel**: visual tests run in parallel; local/devnet serial (`fullyParallel: false`)\n- **Workers**: 1 (for test isolation)\n- **Viewport**: 1280x1080 Desktop Chrome\n- **Traces**: retained on failure (devnet)\n- **Retries**: visual=0; devnet=2\n\n---\n\n### 9. **Test Patterns Observed**\n\n#### **Complete Lifecycle (03-lifecycle.spec.ts)**\n- beforeAll: Fund wallets, initialize localnet\n- Player A creates match\n- On-chain verify: match PDA in \"waiting\" phase\n- Player B joins\n- Snapshot treasury balance\n- Both wait for backend settlement (30s timeout)\n- On-chain verify: results complementary, match closed, fee received\n- Winner returns to lobby\n\n#### **Error Handling (01-error-flow.spec.ts)**\n- Serial execution (`test.describe.configure({ mode: \"serial\" })`)\n- Test 1: Insufficient balance в†’ create rejected, no PDA\n- Test 2: Join stale match в†’ lobby state preserved\n- Test 3: Settled match в†’ no stale claim/settle actions\n\n#### **Visual Regression (visual/states.spec.ts)**\n- addInitScript to clear localStorage (fresh state)\n- Click wallet button в†’ wait for connected state\n- Re-inject animation freeze\n- 300ms settle\n- Screenshot with optional maxDiffPixelRatio\n\n---\n\n### 10. **Key Insights**\n\n1. **Determinism is foundational**: Fixed seeds for PRNG, Date, crypto, and keypairs ensure reproducible tests.\n2. **Dual-player pattern scales**: Two contexts avoid cross-talk, each with isolated wallet + storage.\n3. **On-chain assertions are critical**: Tests verify not just UI but actual PDA state, fee calculations, and account closure.\n4. **Mock noise filtering prevents flakes**: Expected auth/fetch errors are filtered; real errors still fail tests.\n5. **Serial + retry strategy**: Local tests run serially (state dependency); devnet tests retry up to 2Г— for VRF variance.\n6. **Fixtures are composable**: Root fixture (`stablePage`) + test-type fixtures (`playerAPage`/`playerBPage`) layer cleanly.\n7. **Page objects abstract away selectors**: Tests read like user flows (create в†’ join в†’ claim) rather than low-level DOM manipulation.\n\n---\n\n### File Paths Summary\n\n**Core test files:**\n- `/workspaces/rng-utopia/sources/rng-utopia/apps/platform/e2e/fixtures.ts`\n- `/workspaces/rng-utopia/sources/rng-utopia/apps/platform/e2e/local/fixtures.ts`\n- `/workspaces/rng-utopia/sources/rng-utopia/apps/platform/e2e/local/03-lifecycle.spec.ts`\n- `/workspaces/rng-utopia/sources/rng-utopia/apps/platform/e2e/local/01-error-flow.spec.ts`\n\n**Helper modules:**\n- `/workspaces/rng-utopia/sources/rng-utopia/apps/platform/e2e/local/helpers/page-objects.ts`\n- `/workspaces/rng-utopia/sources/rng-utopia/apps/platform/e2e/local/helpers/on-chain.ts`\n- `/workspaces/rng-utopia/sources/rng-utopia/apps/platform/e2e/local/helpers/wallets.ts`\n- `/workspaces/rng-utopia/sources/rng-utopia/apps/platform/e2e/local/helpers/localnet-setup.ts`\n\n**Configuration:**\n- `/workspaces/rng-utopia/sources/rng-utopia/apps/platform/playwright.config.ts` (visual)\n- `/workspaces/rng-utopia/sources/rng-utopia/apps/platform/playwright.local.config.ts`\n- `/workspaces/rng-utopia/sources/rng-utopia/apps/platform/playwright.devnet.config.ts`\n\n**Scripts:**\n- `/workspaces/rng-utopia/sources/rng-utopia/apps/platform/scripts/run-e2e-local.sh`"}],"totalDurationMs":84528,"totalTokens":74066,"totalToolUseCount":21,"usage":{"input_tokens":0,"cache_creation_input_tokens":666,"cache_read_input_tokens":69191,"output_tokens":4209,"server_tool_use":{"web_search_requests":0,"web_fetch_requests":0},"service_tier":"standard","cache_creation":{"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens":0,"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens":666},"inference_geo":"","iterations":[],"speed":"standard"}}}
