eate matches via the `/fairness/matches/create` endpoint (which also requires JWT)\n  \n- вќЊ No E2E test currently navigates to `/profile`\n  - Smoke test (00-smoke.spec.ts) only checks app load and wallet button\n  - Lifecycle tests focus on game creation/joining, not profile view\n  - You'd need to write a new test\n\n---\n\n### **8. Key Files**\n\n| File | Purpose |\n|------|---------|\n| `/workspaces/rng-utopia/sources/rng-utopia/apps/platform/src/lib/auth-store.ts` | In-memory access token + localStorage refresh token storage |\n| `/workspaces/rng-utopia/sources/rng-utopia/apps/platform/src/context/SessionContext.tsx` | JWT auto-auth on wallet connect, token refresh scheduling |\n| `/workspaces/rng-utopia/sources/rng-utopia/apps/platform/src/lib/auth-api.ts` | Thin fetch wrappers for `/auth/*` endpoints |\n| `/workspaces/rng-utopia/sources/rng-utopia/packages/wallet/src/test/TestWalletProvider.tsx` | Deterministic keypair signing for E2E |\n| `/workspaces/rng-utopia/sources/rng-utopia/apps/platform/e2e/local/fixtures.ts` | Playwright dual-player fixture with seed injection |\n| `/workspaces/rng-utopia/sources/rng-utopia/services/backend/src/routes/auth.ts` | Challenge generation, signature verification, JWT issuance |\n| `/workspaces/rng-utopia/sources/rng-utopia/services/backend/src/routes/profile.ts` | `/profile/transactions` endpoint (requires JWT) |\n| `/workspaces/rng-utopia/sources/rng-utopia/apps/platform/scripts/run-e2e-local.sh` | Local E2E orchestration (validator + backend + tests) |\n| `/workspaces/rng-utopia/sources/rng-utopia/services/backend/src/config.ts` | JWT secret derivation (deterministic in local E2E) |"}],"totalDurationMs":137686,"totalTokens":68965,"totalToolUseCount":38,"usage":{"input_tokens":0,"cache_creation_input_tokens":366,"cache_read_input_tokens":66624,"output_tokens":1975,"server_tool_use":{"web_search_requests":0,"web_fetch_requests":0},"service_tier":"standard","cache_creation":{"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens":0,"ephemeral_5m_in